Which of the following false statement about iBase Designer?
A. iBase designer allows you to add, modify anddelete entity record data.
B. iBase designer allows you to design databases
C. iBase designer allows you to create new databases
D. iBase designer allows you to administer the database
Answer: A
Which of these is not listed in the release notes as a supported SQL Server version for
iBase 8.9.1?
A. SQL Server 2008 R2
B. SQL Server 2008
C. SQL Server 2005
D. SQL Server 2000
Answer: D
Which statement is False about Alert definitions?
A. Alert definitions are created andedited by the iBase designer using the alerting
configuration tool
B. iBase users create and edit Alert definitions
C. iBase users can unsubscribe from Alert Definitions
D. Alert definitions are automatically deleted if a change to the entity and link types in the
database makes the alert definition invalid
Answer: A
